      "id": "PopularPost345489",
      "post_content": "Not true, Metal. Those other cards allow the caster the choice of whether to pay or not. They can let the spell be countered and continue to pay and play for something else. This one forces them to tap all lands, effectively shutting down their turn ( provided the X is paid high enough. )",
      "posted_by": "RedJaron",
